<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="zh-CN"><head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>AI视觉物联网控制系统 · 50大高价值应用场景</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fb;
            color: #1a2639;
            line-height: 1.6;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        /* 头部区域 */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b1e3d 0%, #1b3b5c 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: -100px;
            right: -80px;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 50%;
            bottom: -60px;
            left: -40px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero .badge-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin: 1.8rem 0 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .badge {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 0.45rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        }

        /* 介绍卡片 */
        .intro-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .intro-text {
            flex: 2;
            min-width: 280px;
        }

        .intro-text h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 650;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #0b1e3d;
        }

        .intro-text p {
            color: #334155;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #e9f2ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stat-badge {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            padding: 0.3rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0369a1;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* 筛选栏 */
        .filter-bar {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin: 1.2rem 0 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .filter-btn {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 0.55rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 550;
            color: #334155;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .filter-btn:hover {
            border-color: #2563eb;
            color: #1e40af;
            background: #f0f7ff;
        }

        .filter-btn.active {
            background: #0b1e3d;
            border-color: #0b1e3d;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px -6px rgba(11, 30, 61, 0.4);
        }

        .counter {
            margin-left: auto;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* 场景网格 */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 3rem;
        }

        .scene-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.8rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.25s;
            border: 1px solid #f0f3f8;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .scene-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 35px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-color: #dbeafe;
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .scene-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 18px;
        }

        .category-tag {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: #eef2ff;
            color: #4338ca;
        }

        .scene-title {
            font-weight: 680;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin: 0.6rem 0 0.5rem;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .scene-desc {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .scene-number {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            right: 1.2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        /* 不同类别标签颜色微调 */
        .tag-family {
            background: #fce7f3;
            color: #9d174d;
        }
        .tag-retail {
            background: #fff7ed;
            color: #9a3412;
        }
        .tag-industry {
            background: #f3f0ff;
            color: #4c1d95;
        }
        .tag-agriculture {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #065f46;
        }
        .tag-healthcare {
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        .tag-office {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            color: #075985;
        }
        .tag-transport {
            background: #fffbea;
            color: #854d0e;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .intro-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 主视觉 -->
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>🧠 AI视觉 · 物联网电源控制</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">监控摄像头智能分析画面 → 实时控制物联网设备电源 / 开关<br>从被动录像到主动干预，挖掘超过120个场景，精选50大高价值项目</p>
            <div class="badge-group">
                <span class="badge">🔌 智能插座/继电器控制</span>
                <span class="badge">📹 边缘AI视频分析</span>
                <span class="badge">🌐 物联网设备直控</span>
                <span class="badge">⚡ 毫秒级联动</span>
                <span class="badge">🏭 工业级可靠性</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 技术简介 -->
        <div class="intro-card">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <h2>📋 项目核心逻辑</h2>
                <p><span class="stat-badge">视觉感知</span> 摄像头实时捕捉画面 → <span class="stat-badge">AI分析</span> 目标检测、行为识别、状态判断 → <span class="stat-badge">规则引擎</span> 匹配控制策略 → <span class="stat-badge">物联执行</span> 通过智能插座/继电器模块/物联网协议直接控制设备电源或开关状态。</p>
                <div class="highlight">
                    ✅ 既可间接控制传统电器（通断电），也可直接控制智能物联网设备（支持WiFi/Zigbee/Modbus等）。系统已挖掘超过120个细分应用场景，以下精选<b>50个最具商业价值</b>的项目。
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 筛选器 -->
        <div class="filter-bar" id="filterBar">
            <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">🔍 全部场景</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="family">🏠 智慧家庭</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="retail">🛒 商业零售</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="industry">⚙️ 工业制造</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="agriculture">🌾 农业养殖</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="healthcare">⚕️ 医疗健康</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="office">💼 办公教育</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="transport">🚆 交通能源</button>
            <span class="counter" id="sceneCounter">显示 51 个场景</span>
        </div>

        <!-- 场景卡片网格 -->
        <div class="grid" id="sceneGrid">
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#1</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">👴</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">老人跌倒自动报警与断电保护</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">检测老人跌倒姿态，立即呼叫紧急联系人并切断周边非必要电器电源，防止二次伤害。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#2</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">👶</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">儿童攀爬窗户自动锁窗</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别小孩靠近窗户或阳台并试图攀爬，自动关闭电动窗锁或触发纱窗电机锁定。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#3</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">💧</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">水龙头忘关溢水关阀</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">视觉识别地面溢水或水槽持续溢流，联动电动球阀自动关闭总水阀。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#4</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🔥</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">厨房火灾/干烧自动断气</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">检测灶台火焰异常、锅具烧干冒烟，自动切断燃气电磁阀或电磁炉电源。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#5</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🪟</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">节能管理</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">开窗时空调自动断电</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别窗户打开且空调运行，延时后自动关闭空调电源或切换至送风模式。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#6</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">💡</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">节能管理</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">夜间走廊精准视觉灯控</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">AI区分人与宠物，人过开灯、人走灯灭，避免宠物误触发，比红外更精准。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#7</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🐕</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">宠物管理</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">宠物进入禁区超声波驱赶</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别猫狗进入沙发、厨房等禁止区域，自动开启超声波驱赶器电源。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#8</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🌧️</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">雨天自动关窗电机</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">室外摄像头识别下雨或雨滴，联动关窗电机，保护室内物品。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#9</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🍼</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">婴幼看护</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">婴儿哭闹自动摇篮白噪音</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">婴儿监控检测哭声，自动启动电动摇篮、播放白噪音或轻音乐。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#10</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🚪</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">智能门禁</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">门口人脸识别门控</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别已授权家庭成员或快递员，自动释放智能门锁电源或开启大门。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="family">
                    <span class="scene-number">#11</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🧯</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-family">家庭安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">家庭火灾烟雾关燃气总阀</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">AI视觉检测室内火焰或浓烟，立即切断燃气管道电磁阀并打开排风扇。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#12</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🏪</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">零售安防</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">商店打烊入侵报警锁门</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">夜间识别店内可疑人员，自动报警并切断非必要照明，同时锁定卷帘门电源。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#13</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🧊</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">冷链管理</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">生鲜冷柜门未关报警保护</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别卧式冷柜门未闭合，发出声光报警并联动冷柜制冷保护模式。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#14</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🛒</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">零售安防</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">无人超市盗窃行为锁门</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别恶意藏匿商品、未付款离店，触发闸机锁闭并报警。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#15</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🖥️</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">智慧营销</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">展厅客户停留触发广告屏</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">检测顾客在某展品前停留超过N秒，自动开启对应介绍屏幕或唤醒服务机器人。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#16</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">👨‍🍳</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">食品安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">餐厅后厨未戴帽/口罩断电</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别厨师未规范佩戴，联动切断对应灶具电源或电磁炉，规范食品安全。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#17</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🏨</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">酒店节能</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">酒店客房入住自动供电</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别客人入住进入房间，自动开启空调、照明、电视插座电源。识别退房离开，延时切断。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#18</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🧾</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">零售运营</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">收银排队过长开启备用收银</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">视觉计数排队&gt;5人，自动点亮备用收银台指示灯并推送通知。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="retail">
                    <span class="scene-number">#19</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">🏛️</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-retail">文博安防</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">贵重展品触摸告警断电</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">检测到有人触摸展柜或展品，触发振动报警并切断展台照明电源警示。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="industry">
                    <span class="scene-number">#20</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">⚠️</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-industry">工业安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">工厂危险区域误入紧急停机</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">识别人员进入机器人工作区或冲压危险区，50ms内切断设备动力电源。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="industry">
                    <span class="scene-number">#21</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="scene-icon">📦</div>
                        <span class="category-tag tag-industry">智能制造</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="scene-title">传送带异物自动分拣剔除</h3>
                    <p class="scene-desc">AI识别大块异物或异色物体，控制气动推杆/挡板电源，精准剔除。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="scene-card" data-category="industry">
                    <span class="scene-number">#22</span>
                    <div class="card-header">
